docs.lead_paragraph: SAN FRANCISCO, July 30. -- The countries which have agreed to exhibit at the Panama-Pacific Exposition are Argentine, Brazil, Bolivia, Canada, China, Costa Rica, San Domingo, Ecuador, France, Guatemala, Hayti, Honduras, Japan, Mexico, Netherlands, Nicaragua, Panama, Peru, Portugal, Salvador, Spain and Uruguay -- twenty-two in all.
